pageProduct.description:
General Information

Linseed oil (Flaxseed oil) capsules with DHA - rich schinzochytrium algal oil

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Common Uses

Omega 3-6-9 flaxseed with DHA rich schizochytrium algal oil providing a plant based, rich source of essential fatty acids to help maintain general health and wellbeing.
This formula:
? Is a natural source of Omega fatty acids an alternative to fish oil
? Supports healthy skin, brain and eye health
? Maintains cardiovascular system and heart health
? Supports nervous system health

 

Directions

Take 1-2 capsules daily, or as directed by your health professional
